Privacy Policy for Pawnecct

Last updated: 13/Sept/2023

1. Introduction

Welcome to Pawnecct! This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, share, and protect your personal information when you use our mobile application, website, and services (collectively referred to as "Pawnecct" or the "Service"). By accessing or using Pawnecct, you agree to the terms and practices outlined in this Privacy Policy.

2. Information We Collect

2.1. Information You Provide

When you use Pawnecct, we may collect information you voluntarily provide, such as:

- Account registration details (e.g., name, email address, phone number)
- Profile information (e.g., profile picture)
- Communications with us (e.g., in-app messaging)

2.2. Automatically Collected Information

We may automatically collect certain information, including:

- Device information (e.g., device type, operating system, unique device identifiers)
- Usage data (e.g., app features used, session duration)
- Location information, if you grant us permission

2.3. Cookies and Similar Technologies

Pawnecct may use cookies and similar technologies to enhance your experience, analyze usage patterns, and deliver targeted content and advertisements. You can manage your cookie preferences through your device settings or the app's settings.

3. How We Use Your Information

We may use your information for various purposes, including:

- Providing, maintaining, and improving our services
- Customizing content and ads
- Complying with legal obligations
- Protecting our rights and interests

4. Data Sharing

We may share your information with third parties in the following circumstances:

- With your consent
- To comply with legal obligations
- To service providers and partners who assist us in providing the Service
- In connection with business transactions (e.g., mergers, acquisitions)
- To protect our rights and safety

5. Security

We take reasonable measures to protect your information from unauthorized access and disclosure. However, no online or mobile application can be completely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.

6. Your Choices

You have certain rights regarding your personal information. You can:

- Access and update your account information
- Adjust your communication preferences

7. Children's Privacy

Pawnecct is not intended for use by individuals under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.

8. Changes to this Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. We will notify you of any material changes via the app or email.

9. Contact Us

If you have questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us at verygoodrove+pawnnect@gmail.com.
